title: EWZ Crosses Above Key Moving Average Level - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Thursday, shares of the iShares MSCI Brazil ETF (Symbol: EWZ) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $41.90, changing hands as high as $42.35 per share. iShares MSCI Brazil shares are currently trading up about 2.5% on the day.
